did.head: DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY
did.physdesc: Organizational and financial records, architectural plans, photographs, printed materials, and publications.
did.repository: Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library
did.abstract: Records and drawings of work pertaining to the work of Rahn, a landscape architect working in Rochester and Buffalo, New York.

scopecontent.head: COLLECTION DESCRIPTION
scopecontent.p: Records and drawings of work undertaken for clients; also, office files, American Society of Landscape Architects records, blueprints, slides and photographs, certificates, drawings, magazines, catalogs, books, periodicals, cost data books, and other material pertaining to the work of Rahn, a landscape architect working in Rochester and Buffalo, New York.
